Source: tmjos-calamares-branding
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: TMJOs Team <tmjos-archive@tmjsistemas.com.br>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/TMJacometti/TMJOs

Package: tmjos-calamares-branding
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         calamares,
         calamares-settings-debian
Description: TMJOs branding for Calamares installer
 Calamares branding component "tmjos" — provê:
  * branding.desc com strings TMJOs, paleta neon (cyan/magenta/dark navy)
    e referências pros assets locais
  * show.qml — slideshow com 3 slides (boas-vindas, manifesto, slogan)
    exibido durante a instalação
  * logo.png + welcome.png em /usr/share/calamares/branding/tmjos/
 .
 Pra ativar o branding tmjos no installer, edita
 /etc/calamares/settings.conf adicionando ou alterando a linha:
   branding: tmjos
 .
 (O hook live-build do TMJOs faz isso automaticamente na ISO.
 Pra sistema instalado, scripts/tmjos_customize.sh roda o sed.)
